            <section class="character_intro">
                <h2>Dragonborn Sorceror 1</h2>
                <q class="character_flavorText">Do you hear that? It is the roaring in my blood.</q>
                <img class="character_avatar" src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" alt="Character Name (Dragonborn Sorceror)" />
                <div class="content-wrapper">
                    <p>You are a ferocious wanderer of the untrodden ways, a survivor who constantly tests yourself against the dangers of the wild—and conquers.</p>
                    <p>Despite your self-sufficiency, you tire of a life alone. Your clan is far, but these companions are the closest thing to a tribe. As long as they can prove themselves worthy of your company, you will travel with them.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="character_stats">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-6">
                        <h3>Character Name</h3>
                        <i>Medium humanoid (silver dragonborn), draconic bloodline, neutral good</i>
