                        </div>
                        <div class="character_proficiencies">
                            <div class="content-wrapper">
                                <p><b>Proficiencies</b> (+2 proficiiency bonus)</p>
                                <p><b>Saving Throws:</b> Con +4, Cha +5</p>
                                <p><b>Skills:</b> Arcana +2, Athletics +2, Intimidation +5, Survival +3</p>
